high_descs: Turn right and walk to the white table on the left.
Pick up the spatula to the left of the clear bottle on the table.
Turn around and walk to the sink on the right.
Put the spatula inside the sink, rinse it for a few seconds and pick it back up.
Turn around and walk to the white table on the left.
Put the rinsed spatula to the left of the clear bottle on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed spatula on a table.

high_descs: Turn right and go the counter and turn left to face the counter
Pick up the spatula from in front of the bowl on the counter
Turn around and take a step then turn right and go to the sink
Put the spatula in the sink and turn on the water, then turn off the water and take the spatula out of the sink
Turn around and go as far as the stool that is on the right, then turn left and go to the table
Put the spatula to the left of the bottle on the table
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned spatula on the table

high_descs: Turn right and move to face the white table.
Pick up the spatula nearest to you on the white table.
Turn left and move to the sink at the other end of the kitchen.
Place the spatula in the sink, rinse the spatula in the sink, and then pick up the spatula again.
Turn around and move back to the white table to the right of the refrigerator.
Place the spatula on the white table to the right of the spoon.
anns.task_desc: Rinse the spatula sitting on the white table and put it back.
